14:21.425 --> 14:23.384
I just said it was hard.All right, all right.

14:23.427 --> 14:25.299
I was just working with
what you were giving me.

14:25.342 --> 14:27.649
Another soda?

14:27.692 --> 14:29.346
I'm good.

14:34.482 --> 14:36.223
So what's to stop me from just

14:36.266 --> 14:37.789
making a run for it right now?

14:37.833 --> 14:39.443
Nothing, really.

14:39.487 --> 14:41.619
But it's 110
degrees out there

14:41.663 --> 14:43.447
and we're in the
middle of nowhere.

14:43.491 --> 14:46.233
Right. Right.

14:56.765 --> 14:59.333
[cheering]

15:01.988 --> 15:03.337
Yo-leven![cheering]

15:06.340 --> 15:09.299
Don't you leave, sugar,
you're my good luck.

15:09.343 --> 15:10.648
Let her ride!

15:10.692 --> 15:12.694
[cheering]

15:20.397 --> 15:22.443
[gasping]

15:22.486 --> 15:25.489
It's...

15:25.533 --> 15:27.361
hot out there.

15:33.323 --> 15:34.890
You see any snakes?

15:34.934 --> 15:36.283
Six.

15:36.326 --> 15:37.545
Yeah.

15:43.594 --> 15:45.292
Come on, baby, work with me.

15:45.335 --> 15:47.685
Anything but seven.
Anything but seven.

15:49.383 --> 15:50.558
Seven out.

15:50.601 --> 15:53.996
No! That's my mom's bail money!

15:54.040 --> 15:56.303
I can give you a coupon
to the buffet.

15:56.346 --> 15:59.175
Can I bet it?

16:02.700 --> 16:04.137
You are paying me
a hundred dollars an hour;

16:04.180 --> 16:05.921
at some point, we should
probably work on your serve.

16:05.965 --> 16:08.010
Oh, please, we both know

16:08.054 --> 16:09.620
I'm a better tennis
player than you.

16:10.839 --> 16:12.841
[ringtone plays]

16:14.060 --> 16:15.626
[sighs]

16:15.670 --> 16:17.019
Oh, my God, what?

16:17.063 --> 16:19.195
I'm in the middle of
a tennis lesson.

16:19.239 --> 16:21.502
I am so sorry,
but it's an emergency.

16:21.545 --> 16:23.025
My mom just got arrested

16:23.069 --> 16:24.679
and I need to borrow
two grand for bail.

16:24.722 --> 16:26.898
Arrested?CHRISTY: Yeah.

16:26.942 --> 16:28.683
It happened five minutes ago.

16:28.726 --> 16:30.902
You're the first person
I thought of to call.

16:30.946 --> 16:33.427
Aw. Aw.

16:35.211 --> 16:37.170
Text me something
about your account.

16:37.213 --> 16:39.085
I got to go. Bye.

16:43.437 --> 16:44.960
This is her last year.

16:45.004 --> 16:46.570
She's adorable.

16:46.614 --> 16:48.485
This is her now.

16:48.529 --> 16:50.922
Wow, that's a lot
of eyeliner.

16:50.966 --> 16:53.708
Yeah, and you
really notice it

16:53.751 --> 16:55.927
since she shaved
her head.

16:55.971 --> 16:59.322
Uh, Christy was a pretty
difficult teenager, too,

16:59.366 --> 17:02.195
though some of that was
hormones from the pregnancy.

17:02.238 --> 17:04.240
Oh, God.
Just keep trying.

17:04.284 --> 17:05.763
She's gonna keep
pushing you away,

17:05.807 --> 17:08.070
but one day that bedroom
door will open again

17:08.114 --> 17:10.029
and she'll be glad
you're standing there.

17:10.072 --> 17:11.247
I hope you're right.

17:11.291 --> 17:14.076
I'm always right.

17:14.120 --> 17:16.165
Never in a million years
would I have thought

17:16.209 --> 17:18.080
I'd have such a wonderful,
loving relationship

17:18.124 --> 17:19.603
with my daughter.CHRISTY: Mom.

17:19.647 --> 17:20.909
Where the hell have you been?

17:20.952 --> 17:22.606
I thought you left me here
to rot!

17:22.650 --> 17:25.218
Darling.

17:25.261 --> 17:26.741
I'm sorry.

17:26.784 --> 17:28.699
We'll talk about it in the car.
Pay the man.

17:28.743 --> 17:30.397
I can't.

17:32.790 --> 17:36.185
Oh, God, Christy,
you gambled Adam's money.

17:36.229 --> 17:38.361
I did.
[sighs]

17:38.405 --> 17:40.102
So then I called Jill.

17:40.146 --> 17:43.236
And you gambled
Jill's money, too?

17:43.279 --> 17:46.065
It all happened so fast.

17:46.108 --> 17:49.807
I'm not sure
I understand pai gow.

17:49.851 --> 17:53.811
So what, I'm gonna do hard time
for parking tickets?

17:53.855 --> 17:56.205
Yes... 'cause your
daughter's a loser.

17:56.249 --> 17:58.120
That's why Patrick didn't
want to be with me,

17:58.164 --> 17:59.861
that's why I didn't
get into law school,

17:59.904 --> 18:01.645
that's why I hit
on a soft 19.

18:01.689 --> 18:05.171
Oof.I know, right?

18:05.214 --> 18:09.175
Okay. Well, what time's dinner?

18:09.218 --> 18:11.090
You know, Bonnie,

18:11.133 --> 18:14.005
these computers
can be a bit glitchy.

18:14.049 --> 18:15.659
Damn it, Gene,
I've got enough on my plate

18:15.703 --> 18:18.401
without worrying
about your problems.

18:18.445 --> 18:20.664
I'm saying,

18:20.708 --> 18:22.927
maybe your arrest record

18:22.971 --> 18:24.842
somehow disappeared.

18:24.886 --> 18:26.322
How about...

18:26.366 --> 18:28.324
you take care
of your daughter,

18:28.368 --> 18:30.152
I'll go take care of mine?

18:30.196 --> 18:31.371
Really?

18:31.414 --> 18:32.763
Really.

18:32.807 --> 18:34.417
Christy, go outside and
pull the car right up

18:34.461 --> 18:36.419
to the front door and blast
the air conditioning.

18:36.463 --> 18:38.073
That I can do.

18:38.117 --> 18:39.901
Watch out for snakes.

18:43.905 --> 18:45.124
Thank you.

18:46.560 --> 18:47.952
And hang in there
with your daughter.

18:47.996 --> 18:49.345
Don't be discouraged by this.

18:49.389 --> 18:50.520
Roger that.

18:50.564 --> 18:52.131
Bonnie?

18:52.174 --> 18:53.262
Yeah.

18:53.306 --> 18:56.265
Never come back to Nevada.

18:56.309 --> 18:58.789
I'll add it to the list.

19:06.841 --> 19:08.669
Hey, you missed
the exit for the spa.

19:08.712 --> 19:09.931
We can't go to the spa.

19:09.974 --> 19:11.019
Why not?

19:11.062 --> 19:12.412
Because I don't deserve it.

19:13.717 --> 19:16.155
Stupid pai gow.

19:16.198 --> 19:17.765
I do.
I'm covered in jail stink,

19:17.808 --> 19:19.027
and I'm getting
a salt scrub.

19:19.070 --> 19:20.550
I don't know what it is,
I may hate it,

19:20.594 --> 19:21.943
but I'm getting it.

19:21.986 --> 19:23.727
Followed by a selection
of artisanal cheeses

19:23.771 --> 19:25.207
I saw on the website.

19:26.556 --> 19:28.254
That does sound nice.

19:28.297 --> 19:29.951
Oh, no cheese for you.
You're staying in the room.

19:29.994 --> 19:31.779
You can look out the window,
but only at the parking lot,

19:31.822 --> 19:33.041
not at the mountain.

19:34.347 --> 19:36.087
That seems fair.

19:36.131 --> 19:38.394
Okay, I'll double back.

19:44.661 --> 19:46.620
[siren chirps]

19:46.663 --> 19:48.230
Son of a bitch.

19:48.274 --> 19:50.580
You didn't do anything illegal
in Nevada, did you?

19:52.278 --> 19:54.062
I guess we're gonna find out.

